repository-code: "https://github.com/aiprof202604-tech/soap-sbar-llm-benchmark"
abstract: >-
  Companion archive to the manuscript "Fact-Transcription Fidelity in Large
  Language Model SOAP-to-SBAR Translation: A Three-Stage Automated Evaluation
  Across Three Vendors". Contains the nine source SOAP scenarios, 180 fact
  tags, 1,620 generated SBAR records, three-stage judging outputs, alternative-
  arbiter sensitivity analysis, and the analysis scripts that reproduce all
  numerical results reported in the manuscript.
